title: Jack Straker
text: Jack Straker (born 13 April 1993 in <a href="Australia">Australia</a>) is an <a href="Australian">Australian</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who plays for the <a href="Queensland%20Reds">Queensland Reds</a> in <a href="Super%20Rugby">Super Rugby</a>. His playing position is <a href="Prop%20%28rugby%20union%29">prop</a>. He was a late inclusion in the Reds squad for round 7 in 2020.
